WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.208 --> 00:00:10.000
Brave capsule dwellers,

2
00:00:10.291 --> 00:00:13.083
Another year in the capsule is quickly approaching

3
00:00:13.375 --> 00:00:15.416
The daily routine is finely tuned to perfection

4
00:00:15.666 --> 00:00:17.791
Every detail falls into place

5
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.791
Routine rules

6
00:00:20.083 --> 00:00:22.000
The captains have done an excellent job

7
00:00:22.291 --> 00:00:25.041
Unity reigns in every capsule

8
00:00:25.416 --> 00:00:29.041
Community spaces host lectures and debates

9
00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:32.416
Vigorous brainstorming for the future is underway

10
00:00:32.833 --> 00:00:35.833
What kind of world, what kind of society do they want

11
00:00:36.083 --> 00:00:39.125
to see at the end of the Vivaarium experiment?

12
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.666
As a result of Silver's collective vote,

13
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.041
Estonians will remain settled in the future

14
00:00:45.416 --> 00:00:48.708
The home courtyard becomes the center of life once again,

15
00:00:49.083 --> 00:00:51.583
as every Estonian is guaranteed

16
00:00:51.833 --> 00:00:54.000
a piece of land.

17
00:00:54.416 --> 00:00:56.750
At the same time, this pushes out

18
00:00:56.958 --> 00:00:59.291
all kinds of foreign species

19
00:00:59.583 --> 00:01:02.958
The Estonian language is preserved better than ever

20
00:01:03.291 --> 00:01:06.666
and the entire capsule rejoices

21
00:01:07.750 --> 00:01:09.791
As a result of Violet's collective vote,

22
00:01:10.166 --> 00:01:13.166
the focus is on procreation

23
00:01:13.458 --> 00:01:16.458
Expect a lot of newborns

24
00:01:16.708 --> 00:01:20.166
Childless individuals contribute to the community

25
00:01:20.458 --> 00:01:23.708
with their time and assist future parents

26
00:01:23.916 --> 00:01:26.208
with preparations

27
00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:28.791
Total unity prevails

28
00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:32.333
As a result of Turquoise's collective vote,

29
00:01:32.583 --> 00:01:35.416
traditional reproduction methods are eliminated

30
00:01:35.958 --> 00:01:38.541
The first purified and enhanced embryos are ready to mature

31
00:01:38.791 --> 00:01:41.375
A new groundbreaking generation is already on its way

32
00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:45.500
And meanwhile, Turquoises

33
00:01:45.958 --> 00:01:48.625
don't have to torture their bodies but can

34
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.500
surf in Vivaverse.

35
00:01:51.791 --> 00:01:53.833
Everyone is content!

36
00:01:54.166 --> 00:01:56.208
All is well!

37
00:01:56.750 --> 00:01:58.791
As a result of Lime's collective vote,

38
00:01:59.375 --> 00:02:02.250
having children has become a paid endeavor

39
00:02:02.875 --> 00:02:05.041
This has a clear impact on the group -

40
00:02:05.375 --> 00:02:07.583
Not a single pregnancy!

41
00:02:07.916 --> 00:02:10.125
Not to mention all the other restrictions

42
00:02:10.625 --> 00:02:13.625
In the Lime capsule, every last expense

43
00:02:14.041 --> 00:02:16.250
has been minimized - even flushing the toilet

44
00:02:16.666 --> 00:02:18.875
occurs once a day

45
00:02:19.666 --> 00:02:21.875
No one complains

46
00:02:22.583 --> 00:02:26.541
Well, actually, there are a few complainers

47
00:02:27.083 --> 00:02:31.041
They vote against the capsule's goals,

48
00:02:31.541 --> 00:02:34.708
they conspire against their capsule mates

49
00:02:35.083 --> 00:02:38.250
Could they become a problem?

50
00:02:38.625 --> 00:02:40.750
Hardly

51
00:02:41.125 --> 00:02:44.083
The captains keep a close eye

52
00:02:44.583 --> 00:02:47.541
on the troublemakers